column5: just curious as to if i can go fishing right now off of linsay or is it closed can i fish closing day
are you talking about Lindsay in the kawarthas??
A few friends have caught some small walleye there the last few weeks...nothing recent though.
If you didn't go, you're too late. The walleye season closed last night at midnight.
You again eh..  How long before you have another melt down this time?
